Hey All, I'm trying to add a separator between links in my main menu. The menu is created with a loop. I added the following after the &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

`{% if depth == 1 and !loop.last %}&lt;span class="navdiv"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;{% endif %}`

It works with the exception of a link that has a sub-menu. Just wondering if anyone knows why?
